name: Josh Baker
cleanBio: Hailing from Manchester, UK, Josh Baker has risen as a versatile DJ and producer, embodying the creative essence of the new wave of electronic artists, of which he sits at the forefront. His fascination with House music ignited at 17, propelling him to shape his passion into a thriving career. His drive and unique talent has lead to performances at world renowned events & venues such as; The Warehouse Project, DC10, Fabric, FUSE, Shelter NL, Koko, Parklife Festival Pikes, and more, expanding his influence beyond performance venues.
